<p>Last week, Cook's 44-year-old estranged husband sweetly gave her performance in Love, Guaranteed a Twitter shout-out: 'Rachael is amazing in this.'</p>

<p>On July 17, the Criminal Minds guest star filed a request with a LA County judge for joint custody of their five-year-old son Theodore Vigo Sullivan and their daughter Charlotte Easton, who turns 7 on September 28.</p>

<p>Daniel officially filed for divorce from Rachael on July 10 - 13 months after they both announced their amicable split.</p>

